Report: Several datasets have been collected on human MMP12 complexed with acetohydroxamic acid (1) and with antraquinone (2), on rat CutA1 (3) and on AphA complexed in turn with Au 2+ (4), adenosine (5) and NAD (6) and on chlorocatechol dioxygenase (7). We have attempted to collect a MAD dataset on the latter crystals (7), but the qualit of the crystals was very poor. The data reported are relative the Fe remote wavelength which was the only one of sufficient quality for data processing. Here are the data collection statistics for the best datasets.
